{"id":595156,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/【立此存照】京东首次承认刘强东涉嫌性侵：声明/","date":"2018-09-08T08:28:23Z","modified":"2018-09-09T00:07:41Z","title":"【立此存照】京东首次承认刘强东涉嫌性侵：声明只发英文，微博大面积禁评","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>2018年9月6日，京东在公司的英文网站上就刘强东涉嫌强奸一案<a href=\"http://jdcorporateblog.com/minnesota-updates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">发表英文声明</a>，首次公开承认刘强东于被明尼苏达州的地方警察带走调查的原因是涉嫌性侵。这份声明没有中文版，京东的官方微博对此也未有任何提及。<strong>引起热议后，大多数发表这则新闻的蓝V账号关闭了相关微博的评论。</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595195 size-medium\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/2018-09-08-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></strong></p>\n<p><strong>中国数字时代 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%88%98%E5%BC%BA%E4%B8%9C\">刘强东性侵案</a></strong></p></blockquote>\n<p>2018年9月2日，京东曾发表声明，称刘强东遭美国警方调查是由于受到了“失实指控”。9月4日，美国警方证实刘强东涉嫌的是强奸，为一级重罪。随后，美国有三家法律公司分别宣布要调查京东是否失实披露刘强东的案情。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东禁评0.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595157\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东禁评0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"2459\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东禁评0.jpg 1104w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东禁评0-64x300.jpg 64w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东禁评0-768x3597.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>截至发稿时，@中国新闻周刊 是极少数尚未关闭评论的账号之一，吸引了大量无处可去的微博用户前去吐槽。以下为部分评论截图：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_595162\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东涉嫌性侵-copy.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-595162\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东涉嫌性侵-copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"3581\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东涉嫌性侵-copy.jpg 1347w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东涉嫌性侵-copy-44x300.jpg 44w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东涉嫌性侵-copy-768x5238.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东涉嫌性侵-copy-150x1024.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>附：京东在英文网站上就刘强东涉嫌性侵一案作出的回应</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_595159\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/京东.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-595159\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/京东.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/京东.jpg 2180w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/京东-300x170.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/京东-768x435.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/京东-1024x580.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">京东官网截图</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,27949],"tags":[16773,34255,14123,19607,8817]}